Third-party Models
------------------
This project bundles rembg models (`u2net.onnx`, `isnet-general-use.onnx`)
and Real-ESRGAN (`realesrgan_x4.onnx`). Those models retain their original
upstream licenses — see the rembg and Real-ESRGAN project pages. This
internal-use license covers only the code in this repository.

